Paper: hep-th/0209135

Date: 2002-09-17

Title: A comment on causality

Authors: Ricardo Bentin

Comments: 10 pages

We start from the well-known form of the interval of the special relativity,stare it, and build up an attempt to implement the causality from it. Somefeatures appear to be new, they involve the mass of the particle and thestructure of space-time.